# Blackjack Pro

Professional Blackjack card counting training simulator with multiple counting systems,
deviation indices, and advanced features.

## Quick Installation

```bash
pip install blackjack-pro
blackjack-pro
```

See INSTALL.md for detailed installation instructions.
